*
* c) Duale di P
* -------------
*
*       max z = -3*w1 + 5*w2 - w3
*       s.t.  +2*w1 - 2*w2 - w3 <= +2
*             +3*w1 + 2*w2 + w3 <= +5
*             -w1 + 5*w2 - 2*w3 <= +4
*             w1, w2 <= 0, w3 >= 0
